title: WTB T206 PSA Graded 5-6.5 All Backs
author: Roulette44

posts.post_title: WTB T206 PSA Graded 5-6.5 All Backs
posts.post_content:
*Hello all - I'm fairly new to the boards but have been collecting a very long time (primarily comic books, but more recently back into baseball cards).

Have done business with a couple of boardies here (thromdog, luke), but also have 1,600 feedback +/- on Ebay (handle is InvestmentGradeKeyComics)

Am working on my T206 set - and primarily looking for the following 100 or so subjects.   Preference is PSA 5-6.5, but will consider anything PSA 4-7.  Any backs are fine, looking for reasonably well centered cards, no qualified cards, please.

Here's the list.   But note that if you have others that fit the above specs, please do shoot me a message or email, I have probably 50-100 subjects in PSA 4/4.5 that i'd like to eventually upgrade.

Happy to buy or trade, depending on your preference.   Have lots of great trade including 300-400 PSA graded T206s, 50 or so PSA graded 1940 Superman Gum extras, and a few other mega keys (Shoeless Joe RC, for example).  and If you're into comic books, well, i'm your guy for golden age and silver age as well (pre-1970 stuff!).

Thanks for looking.  Hope to hear from you!
Best regards
Joey
